{"type":"message","id":"1506d0b6","parentId":"03e12323","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:11:10.072Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了！`agents.list.*.name` 就是 agent 的名字配置。同时还有 `agents.list.*.identity` 可能包含更多身份信息。让我查看 identity 的结构。\n\n不过，用户当前的配置没有 agents.list，只有 agents.defaults。我需要添加一个 agents.list 条目，包含 id 为 \"main\"（因为当前是 main session），并设置 name 为 \"Agent Admin\"。\n\n让我先查看当前配置来确认 main agent 的情况。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf5b2ec4aec4e1df31c044dea8f9f","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.schema.lookup","path":"agents.list.*.identity"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":966,"output":206,"cacheRead":46784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47956,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773648653491}}
