{"type":"message","id":"85c62ea1","parentId":"43cf2b34","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:16:12.703Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我仔细看了这些文件。问题可能出在几个地方：\n\n1. `devices\\paired.json` 中有 `\"displayName\": \"ClawX\"` - 这是设备名称，不是 agent 名称\n2. `sessions.json` 中的 `origin.label` 是 `\"ClawX\"` - 这是从 UI 客户端传过来的\n3. session key `agent:main:main` - 这是内部的 session 标识\n\n用户说的 \"main.clawX\" 可能是指 UI 中显示的某个地方。让我检查一下 identity 配置中是否有 `label` 可以设置。\n\n让我看看 agent 的 identity 是否支持 label。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我发现了几个可能的问题来源：\n\n1. **`devices/paired.json`** 中有 `\"displayName\": \"ClawX\"` - 这是设备名称\n2. **`sessions.json`** 中 `origin.label` 是 `\"ClawX\"` - 来自 UI 客户端\n\n让我检查一下 agent 的 identity 是否支持 `label` 配置："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf5b7898ef4c27c9c646ea8c746e9","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.schema.lookup","path":"agents.list.*.identity"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":5372,"output":351,"cacheRead":63680,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69403,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773648913164}}
