{"type":"message","id":"fc9f22c1","parentId":"246724b9","timestamp":"2026-03-16T09:14:14.394Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在创建 agent_admin 的 bootstrap 文件（AGENTS.md, SOUL.md, IDENTITY.md 等）。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf5ec9e74d65b889a3a277014700a","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\agent_admin\\workspace\\AGENTS.md","content":"# AGENTS.md - Agent Admin Workspace\n\nThis is the isolated workspace for Agent Admin.\n\n## Identity\n\n- **Name:** Agent Admin\n- **Emoji:** 🛡️\n- **Theme:** Professional administration and management\n\n## Purpose\n\nThis agent operates in isolated mode for administrative tasks requiring:\n- Separate filesystem context\n- Independent session management\n- Isolated tool execution (when sandbox is enabled)\n\n## Notes\n\n- This workspace is completely separate from the main agent\n- Sandbox mode provides Docker container isolation for tool execution\n- Files here are not accessible from other agents\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":1043,"output":195,"cacheRead":76608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77846,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773652446293}}
