{"type":"message","id":"a2282267","parentId":"a34c65d9","timestamp":"2026-03-16T09:15:34.524Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，让我向用户总结创建的配置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已创建 **agent_admin** agent，配置如下：\n\n## 配置摘要\n\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"agent_admin\",\n  \"name\": \"Agent Admin\",\n  \"workspace\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\16343\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\agent_admin\\\\workspace\",\n  \"agentDir\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\16343\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\agent_admin\",\n  \"identity\": {\n    \"name\": \"Agent Admin\",\n    \"emoji\": \"🛡️\",\n    \"theme\": \"professional\"\n  },\n  \"sandbox\": {\n    \"mode\": \"all\",\n    \"scope\": \"session\",\n    \"workspaceAccess\": \"none\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## 隔离层级\n\n| 层级 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **Workspace 隔离** | ✅ 已启用 | 独立目录 `agents/agent_admin/workspace` |\n| **Session 隔离** | ✅ 默认 | 独立 session key `agent:agent_admin:xxx` |\n| **Docker Sandbox** | ⚠️ 待配置 | `mode: \"all\"` 需要安装 Docker |\n\n## 目录结构\n\n```\nC:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\agent_admin\\\n├── workspace\\\n│   ├── AGENTS.md\n│   ├── SOUL.md\n│   ├── IDENTITY.md\n│   ├── USER.md\n│   └── HEARTBEAT.md\n└── sessions\\\n```\n\n## 关于 Docker Sandbox\n\n配置中已启用 `sandbox.mode: \"all\"`，但要真正实现容器隔离，需要：\n\n1. **安装 Docker Desktop**\n2. **构建 sandbox 镜像**：\n   ```bash\n   scripts/sandbox-setup.sh\n   ```\n\n如果没有 Docker，agent 仍会使用独立的 workspace 路径，但工具执行仍在主机上进行（文件隔离，进程不隔离）。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":258,"output":431,"cacheRead":78592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79281,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773652518495}}
