{"type":"message","id":"587207f8","parentId":"db000308","timestamp":"2026-03-16T09:18:12.914Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"winget 安装失败了，可能是网络问题。让我给用户提供手动安装的步骤。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"网络问题导致 winget 安装失败。请手动安装 Docker Desktop：\n\n## 手动安装步骤\n\n### 1. 下载 Docker Desktop\n\n直接下载链接：\n- **官网下载**: https://desktop.docker.com/win/main/amd64/Docker%20Desktop%20Installer.exe\n\n### 2. 安装要求\n\n- Windows 10/11 64位\n- 启用 WSL 2 或 Hyper-V（安装程序会提示）\n- BIOS 中启用虚拟化\n\n### 3. 安装后配置\n\n安装完成并启动 Docker Desktop 后，需要构建 sandbox 镜像："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf5f04d04c119b14f2242f5cf22a2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\ClawX\\resources\\openclaw\\scripts"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":626,"output":195,"cacheRead":79296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80117,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773652680489}}
