{"type":"message","id":"9217c2cb","parentId":"82478b18","timestamp":"2026-03-16T09:21:21.130Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"sandbox explain 显示配置已经正确设置：\n- runtime: sandboxed\n- mode: all\n- scope: session\n- workspaceAccess: none\n\n但是没有 Docker 运行的情况下，sandbox 实际上无法工作。需要安装 Docker Desktop。让我总结一下安装步骤并指导用户。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"配置已正确识别，但实际进程隔离需要 Docker。当前状态：\n\n```\nEffective sandbox:\n  agentId: agent_admin\n  runtime: sandboxed\n  mode: all scope: session\n  workspaceAccess: none\n```\n\n## 实现进程隔离步骤\n\n### 步骤 1：安装 Docker Desktop\n\n请手动下载安装：\n\n👉 **下载链接**: https://desktop.docker.com/win/main/amd64/Docker%20Desktop%20Installer.exe\n\n安装要求：\n- Windows 10/11 64位\n- BIOS 中启用虚拟化\n- 可能需要启用 WSL 2（安装程序会提示）\n\n### 步骤 2：启动 Docker Desktop\n\n安装完成后启动 Docker Desktop，等待左下角显示 \"Docker Desktop is running\"\n\n### 步骤 3：构建 Sandbox 镜像\n\nDocker 运行后，从 GitHub 获取 Dockerfile 并构建："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf5f32c7a77e1c2c1d8edca77daeb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"New-Item -ItemType Directory -Force -Path \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\sandbox\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":1226,"output":342,"cacheRead":89984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91552,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773652857039}}
{"type":"message","id":"b676c719","parentId":"9217c2cb","timestamp":"2026-03-16T09:21:21.354Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019cf5f32c7a77e1c2c1d8edca77daeb","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ŀ¼: C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\nd-----         2026/3/16     17:21                sandbox"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":217,"aggregated":"Ŀ¼: C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\nd-----         2026/3/16     17:21                sandbox","cwd":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773652881351}}
{"type":"message","id":"c3a698f4","parentId":"b676c719","timestamp":"2026-03-16T09:21:40.300Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要创建一个 Dockerfile 来构建 sandbox 镜像。根据文档，默认镜像是 `openclaw-sandbox:bookworm-slim`，基于 debian bookworm slim。让我创建一个基本的 Dockerfile。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf5f36b42619991d043b1645bc53f","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# OpenClaw Sandbox Image\n# Based on Debian Bookworm Slim\nFROM debian:bookworm-slim\n\n# Install basic tools\nRUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \\\n    ca-certificates \\\n    curl \\\n    git \\\n    jq \\\n    procps \\\n    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*\n\n# Create workspace directory\nRUN mkdir -p /workspace && chmod 777 /workspace\n\n# Create non-root user\nRUN useradd -m -u 1000 -s /bin/bash sandbox\n\nWORKDIR /workspace\n\n# Default to sandbox user\nUSER sandbox\n\nENV LANG=C.UTF-8\nENV LC_ALL=C.UTF-8\n","path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\Dockerfile.sandbox"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":346,"output":268,"cacheRead":91200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91814,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773652881356}}
