{"type":"message","id":"ccba7b61","parentId":"34f44b2e","timestamp":"2026-03-16T09:22:20.799Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我创建了一个基本的 Dockerfile。现在我需要给用户一个完整的指令，告诉他们安装 Docker 后如何构建镜像。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf5f3f2045bddfc190dda06f58f10","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Sandbox Setup Instructions\n\n## 1. Install Docker Desktop\n\nDownload and install from:\nhttps://desktop.docker.com/win/main/amd64/Docker%20Desktop%20Installer.exe\n\nAfter installation:\n- Restart computer if prompted\n- Start Docker Desktop\n- Wait until the status shows \"Docker Desktop is running\"\n\n## 2. Build the Sandbox Image\n\nOpen PowerShell and run:\n\n```powershell\ncd $env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\sandbox\ndocker build -t openclaw-sandbox:bookworm-slim -f Dockerfile.sandbox .\n```\n\n## 3. Verify the Image\n\n```powershell\ndocker images | findstr openclaw-sandbox\n```\n\n## 4. Restart OpenClaw Gateway\n\n```powershell\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n## 5. Verify Sandbox is Working\n\n```powershell\nopenclaw sandbox list\nopenclaw sandbox explain --agent agent_admin\n```\n\n## Optional: Build Enhanced Image with More Tools\n\nIf you need Python, Node.js, and other common tools:\n\n```dockerfile\nFROM debian:bookworm-slim\n\nRUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \\\n    ca-certificates \\\n    curl \\\n    git \\\n    jq \\\n    procps \\\n    python3 \\\n    python3-pip \\\n    nodejs \\\n    npm \\\n    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*\n\nRUN mkdir -p /workspace && chmod 777 /workspace\nRUN useradd -m -u 1000 -s /bin/bash sandbox\n\nWORKDIR /workspace\nUSER sandbox\n\nENV LANG=C.UTF-8\nENV LC_ALL=C.UTF-8\n```\n\nBuild with:\n```powershell\ndocker build -t openclaw-sandbox-common:bookworm-slim -f Dockerfile.common .\n```\n\nThen update config:\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [{\n      \"id\": \"agent_admin\",\n      \"sandbox\": {\n        \"docker\": {\n          \"image\": \"openclaw-sandbox-common:bookworm-slim\"\n        }\n      }\n    }]\n  }\n}\n```\n","path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\README.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":277,"output":526,"cacheRead":91520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92323,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773652900313}}
