{"type":"message","id":"4ce95a74","parentId":"094e8b36","timestamp":"2026-03-16T09:22:37.299Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经创建了 Dockerfile 和 README。现在让我给用户一个清晰的总结。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已准备好所有配置文件。\n\n---\n\n## 总结\n\n### 当前状态\n\n| 组件 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **agent_admin agent** | ✅ 已创建 | 独立 workspace 配置完成 |\n| **Sandbox 配置** | ✅ 已配置 | `mode: \"all\"`, `scope: \"session\"` |\n| **Docker Desktop** | ❌ 未安装 | 需要手动安装 |\n| **Sandbox 镜像** | ⏳ 待构建 | Dockerfile 已准备 |\n\n### 下一步操作\n\n**1. 安装 Docker Desktop**\n\n👉 下载：https://desktop.docker.com/win/main/amd64/Docker%20Desktop%20Installer.exe\n\n**2. Docker 启动后，构建镜像**：\n\n```powershell\ncd $env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\sandbox\ndocker build -t openclaw-sandbox:bookworm-slim -f Dockerfile.sandbox .\n```\n\n**3. 重启 OpenClaw**：\n\n```powershell\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n### 进程隔离效果\n\n安装完成后，`agent_admin` 将实现：\n\n- ✅ **独立文件系统** - sandbox 容器内的 `/workspace` 与主机隔离\n- ✅ **独立进程空间** - 所有工具在容器内执行\n- ✅ **网络隔离** - 默认无网络访问\n- ✅ **资源限制** - 可配置 CPU/内存限制\n- ✅ **工具策略** - 可独立配置允许/禁止的工具\n\n详细说明已保存在 `C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\README.md`"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":548,"output":385,"cacheRead":91776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92709,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773652940815}}
